name: UInterchangeVariantSetNode
doc: Class to represent a set of variants.

methods.name: AddCustomDependencyUid
methods.doc: Add the specified translated node's unique ID to this VariantSet.

methods.name: GetCustomDependencyUid
methods.doc: Retrieve the specified translated node's unique ID for this VariantSet.

methods.name: GetCustomDependencyUidCount
methods.doc: Retrieve the number of translated node's unique IDs for this VariantSet.

methods.name: GetCustomDependencyUids
methods.doc: Retrieve all the translated node's unique IDs for this VariantSet.

methods.name: GetCustomDisplayText
methods.doc: Retrieve the text that is displayed in the UI for this VariantSet.

methods.name: GetCustomVariantsPayloadKey
methods.doc: Get the payload key needed to retrieve the variants for this VariantSet.

methods.name: RemoveCustomDependencyUid
methods.doc: Remove the specified translated node's unique ID from this VariantSet.

methods.name: SetCustomDisplayText
methods.doc: Set the text to be displayed in the UI for this VariantSet.

methods.name: SetCustomVariantsPayloadKey
methods.doc: Set the payload key needed to retrieve the variants for this VariantSet.
